snippet.title: Eldritch Climb - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2645670/
Join our Discord server https://discord.gg/Ceb8m2dG53

Learn more on http://www.eldritchclimb.com

Embark in a roguelike climbing adventure! Fight devious creatures, use eccentric items, and try to keep your sanity as you face death over and over again. There are Lovecraftian Horrors waiting to be unveiled... Can you hear the calling?
